<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/L%E1%BB%97-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Li%C3%AAn-ngh%C4%A9a-b%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF-T%E1%BA%A7n/poem-78QDbIP5U2LQIP2zU2OJ5A">Lỗ Trọng Liên nghĩa bất đế Tần - 魯仲連義不帝秦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-c%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-du-Long-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%A1n/poem-HI6X83FIVEfPapQp9WMEuQ">Nhâm Tuất cửu nhật du Long Đại sơn - 壬戌九日遊隆代山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%A9y-binh-m%C3%A3/poem-FUAf_FEoWRmR--1bm7spSA">Tẩy binh mã - 洗兵馬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hy-Hi%E1%BB%81n/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-x_jmofswAbqFZjgEGPaP_g">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hy-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-mriY_zga4scEJQWPV40NeQ">Vương Hy Hiền</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
